title: The Truth About Polio Vaccinations
description: Wild Polio is a terrible disease, but a new strand of Polio has formed from oral vaccinations created to prevent the wild strand. Raymond Francis sheds light on how the vaccine-derived polio virus is on the rise and threatens global health.
